# Implementation Plan - UI Polish and Alerts Sorting

This plan focuses on improving the Alerts page sorting and specific UI alignment and color consistency across the application.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> This plan focuses exclusively on the following three requirements as per your latest request.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Sorting on Alerts Page
Implement sorting for the main Alerts (Bevakningar) page to match the Stock page functionality.

#### [MODIFY] [MainViewModel.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainViewModel.kt)
- Add state for `alertSortMode`.
- Implement sorting of the `watchItemUiState` list using `SortHelper`.

#### [MODIFY] [MainActivity.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainActivity.kt)
- Add sorting menu options to the toolbar when the Alerts tab is active.
- Handle sort mode changes by updating the [MainViewModel](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/MainViewModel.kt#12-435).

---

### 2. Toggle Alignment
Ensure toggle switches in all cards are perfectly top-aligned with the stock name/company name.

#### [MODIFY] [Many files in ui/components/cards/](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/cards/)
- **Toggle Alignment**: In [PriceTargetCard](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/cards/PriceTargetCard.kt#26-121), `MetricAlertCard`, `High52wCard`, `DailyMoveCard`, etc., remove the manual `offset(y = (-6).dp)` from the `Switch`.
- Use `Modifier.align(Alignment.Top)` within the parent [Row](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/components/StockSummaryRow.kt#30-102) to ensure consistent top alignment with the title text.
- Adjust vertical padding if necessary to account for the "invisible pixels" or intrinsic padding of the `Switch` component.

---

### 3. Card Background on Stock Detail Page
Match the background color of alert cards on the stock detail page with the price stat cells.

#### [MODIFY] [AlertAdapter.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/AlertAdapter.kt)
- Add a `containerColor` parameter to the constructor or the [bind](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/AlertAdapter.kt#40-54) method.
- Pass this color down to the `ComposeWatchItemCardWithControls`.

#### [MODIFY] [StockDetailFragment.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/StockDetailFragment.kt)
- When initializing [AlertAdapter](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/AlertAdapter.kt#18-66), pass `MaterialTheme.colorScheme.surfaceVariant` (which matches `@drawable/bg_stat_cell`) as the preferred background color.

#### [MODIFY] [ComposeWatchItemCard.kt](file:///Users/johanlindau/SynologyDrive/Kodprojekt/StockFlip/app/src/main/java/com/stockflip/ui/ComposeWatchItemCard.kt) and Card Components
- Add `containerColor: Color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.surface` to the card composables.
- Use this color instead of the hardcoded `surface`.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. **Sorting**: Go to the "Bevakningar" tab, change sort mode in the menu, and verify the list reorders accordingly.
2. **Toggle Alignment**: Visually inspect alert cards on both the main list and detail pages. The top of the switch should line up precisely with the top of the company name text.
3. **Card Background**: Open a stock detail page. Verify that the alert cards in the "Befintliga bevakningar" section have the same light gray/variant background as the "Senaste pris" and "Nedgång från topp" cells.
